- [ ] Locate `lessons` table schema (e.g. `docs/schema.lessons.sql` or `docs/migrations/`)
- [ ] Ensure `status` column exists with enum: `draft`, `waiting_review`, `published`
- [ ] If missing: add migration in `docs/migrations/`


#### 1.2 Ensure metadata column for canonical keys
- [ ] Verify `lessons` (or equivalent) can store `metadata` JSONB with `canonical_node_key` and `run_id`
- [ ] Required for P7 telemetry loop: CMS → LaDy feedback


